<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Abdur Rehman | Software Engineer</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Portfolio of Abdur Rehman, Software Engineer focused on full-stack web development, e-commerce systems, APIs, and scalable applications." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1020;
      --bg-soft: #121938;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --text: #edf2ff;
      --muted: #b9c2e6;
      --accent: #7c9cff;
      --accent-2: #67e8f9;
      --success: #86efac;
      --shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      --radius: 22px;
      --max: 1120px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(124,156,255,0.2), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(103,232,249,0.14), transparent 20%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #08101f 0%, #0b1020 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .container { width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max)); margin: 0 auto; }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background: rgba(8, 12, 25, 0.72);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 16px 0;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .brand span { color: var(--accent-2); }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 28px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.35fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hero-card, .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 34px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -60px -80px auto;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,156,255,0.28), transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .lead {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.06rem;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0 28px;
    }

    .pill {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #dfe6ff;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform .15s ease, opacity .15s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: #08101f;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .stats {
      padding: 28px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .stat-box {
      padding: 18px 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .stat-value {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    section {
      padding: 26px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .subtext {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 6px 0 0;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .muted { color: var(--muted); }

    ul.clean {
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 22px;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .timeline-date {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .project-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    .project-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .project-tags span {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .project-actions {
      margin-top: auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .small-link {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .grid-2 > .project-card--span-2 {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .project-gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 260px), 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .project-gallery figure {
      margin: 0;
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
      cursor: zoom-in;
      transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), box-shadow 0.35s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    }

    .project-gallery img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      vertical-align: bottom;
    }

    .project-gallery figcaption {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.4;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .project-gallery figure:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      border-color: rgba(124, 156, 255, 0.35);
    }

    .project-gallery figure:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent-2);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .project-gallery figure::after {
      content: "Click to enlarge";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto 10px 48px 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      text-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(6px);
      transition: opacity 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .project-gallery figure:hover::after,
    .project-gallery figure:focus-visible::after {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .project-alias {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 4px 0 0;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      position: relative;
      padding: 4px 0;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .card,
    .hero-card,
    .timeline-item {
      transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), box-shadow 0.35s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    }

    .card:hover,
    .timeline-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(124, 156, 255, 0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    }

    .hero-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.2);
    }

    .reveal-on-scroll {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(28px);
      transition: opacity 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), transform 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
    }

    .reveal-on-scroll.reveal-visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 10000;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.32s ease, visibility 0.32s ease;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox.is-open {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__backdrop {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(4, 8, 18, 0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      cursor: zoom-out;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__dialog {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: min(1200px, 96vw);
      width: 100%;
      animation: lightboxPop 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
    }

    @keyframes lightboxPop {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.94) translateY(12px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__figure {
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__img {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: min(78vh, 820px);
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__caption {
      margin: 14px auto 0;
      max-width: 640px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__counter {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(185, 194, 230, 0.75);
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__close,
    .portfolio-lightbox__nav {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 3;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      background: rgba(18, 25, 56, 0.85);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__close:hover,
    .portfolio-lightbox__nav:hover {
      background: rgba(124, 156, 255, 0.25);
      border-color: rgba(124, 156, 255, 0.45);
      transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.06);
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__close {
      top: -8px;
      right: -8px;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__nav {
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__nav--prev {
      left: -12px;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__nav--next {
      right: -12px;
    }

    .portfolio-lightbox__nav.is-hidden {
      display: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .portfolio-lightbox__nav--prev {
        left: 4px;
      }
      .portfolio-lightbox__nav--next {
        right: 4px;
      }
      .portfolio-lightbox__close {
        top: 8px;
        right: 8px;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
      }
      .reveal-on-scroll {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: none;
      }
    }

    .next-steps li { margin-bottom: 10px; }

    .footer {
      padding: 32px 0 48px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .notice {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: rgba(134,239,172,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(134,239,172,0.2);
      color: #dcffe8;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .hero-grid, .grid-3, .grid-2, .timeline-item {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .hero { padding-top: 42px; }
      .hero-card, .stats, .card { padding: 22px; }
      .section-head { align-items: start; flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <div class="brand">Abdur <span>Rehman</span></div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="hero container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Software Engineer • Full-Stack Web Development • E-commerce Systems</div>
        <h1>Building practical software that solves real business problems.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          I am a software engineer focused on full-stack web development, APIs, automation, and e-commerce applications.
          My work combines clean frontend experiences with reliable backend logic, integrations, and scalable system design.
        </p>

        <div class="pill-row">
          <div class="pill">JavaScript</div>
          <div class="pill">Node.js</div>
          <div class="pill">React</div>
          <div class="pill">Next.js</div>
          <div class="pill">Remix</div>
          <div class="pill">SQL</div>
          <div class="pill">Shopify APIs</div>
          <div class="pill">Python</div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:pc18050.abdurehman@gmail.com">Contact Me</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://github.com/abdurehman370" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/abdu-rehman-b19893288/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="stats hero-card">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Current focus</div>
          <div class="stat-value">Software Engineer / Full-Stack Roles</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Core strengths</div>
          <div class="stat-value">APIs, e-commerce systems, dashboards, automation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Open to</div>
          <div class="stat-value">Corporate, product, GCC, and international opportunities</div>
        </div>
        <div class="notice">
          Replace project demo links below with your actual GitHub repositories or live deployments before applying widely.
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section id="about">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <h2>About</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">
          I have hands-on experience building web and mobile applications, Shopify apps, internal tools, and automation workflows.
          My background includes frontend development, backend APIs, third-party integrations, data scraping, and product-oriented problem solving.
          I enjoy building software that is fast, maintainable, and useful in real business environments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <h2>Skills</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Frontend</h3>
          <p class="muted">React, Next.js, Remix, TypeScript, HTML5, CSS3, Tailwind CSS, Recharts, JavaScript</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Backend</h3>
          <p class="muted">Node.js, Express, Python, FastAPI, REST APIs, GraphQL APIs, webhooks, authentication, automation logic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Data & Tools</h3>
          <p class="muted">PostgreSQL, Prisma ORM, MySQL, SQL Server, Redis, BullMQ, Docker, Git, GitHub, Python scraping, VS Code, API integrations</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <h2>Featured Projects</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <article class="card project-card project-card--span-2">
          <div>
            <h3>I-Car Price Evaluation Platform</h3>
            <p class="muted">Real-time car price evaluation platform for UAE, Lebanon, and Europe markets, combining web, mobile, scraping, and AI-assisted pricing workflows. Implemented Redis and BullMQ to power alert delivery and cron-style scheduled jobs. Includes a verified dealer portal for inventory and listings, plus an admin portal for onboarding and oversight.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span>Next.js</span><span>React Native</span><span>Python</span><span>Redis</span><span>BullMQ</span><span>AI Integration</span><span>Admin Panel</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="clean">
            <li>Built web and mobile product flows for vehicle price prediction.</li>
            <li>Collected listing data from regional sources using Python scrapers.</li>
            <li>Implemented Redis and BullMQ for alerts, background work, and cron job scheduling.</li>
            <li>Implemented dealer authentication and admin controls.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="project-gallery" aria-label="iCar dealer and admin portal screenshots">
            <figure>
              <img src="images/Screenshot from 2026-04-03 18-56-41.png" alt="iCar marketing landing page with dealer login and live market analysis" loading="lazy" />
              <figcaption>Landing — dealer entry and live market positioning</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure>
              <img src="images/Screenshot from 2026-04-03 18-57-06.png" alt="iCar dealer portal sign-in screen" loading="lazy" />
              <figcaption>Dealer portal — secure sign-in</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure>
              <img src="images/Screenshot from 2026-04-03 18-57-31.png" alt="Dealer dashboard showing active listings and inventory metrics" loading="lazy" />
              <figcaption>Dealer dashboard — listings, inventory value, and vehicle management</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure>
              <img src="images/Screenshot from 2026-04-03 19-17-07.png" alt="Admin portal dealers table with status and contact details" loading="lazy" />
              <figcaption>Admin portal — dealer directory and approval status</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure>
              <img src="images/Screenshot from 2026-04-03 19-17-24.png" alt="Admin dealer registrations queue with pending and approved counts" loading="lazy" />
              <figcaption>Admin portal — review and approve dealer registrations</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
          <div class="project-actions">
            <a class="small-link" href="https://github.com/abdurehman370/I-Car" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
            <a class="small-link" href="https://youtu.be/9dU3dyGEr3o" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">YouTube: marketplace scraping</a>
            <a class="small-link" href="https://youtu.be/ijQPD66E8FY" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">YouTube: pricing &amp; listings</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card project-card project-card--span-2">
          <div>
            <h3>ProcureAI: Smart Inventory &amp; Supply Chain Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="project-alias">Alternate product names: SentinelProcure · OptiSource — procurement &amp; inventory intelligence.</p>
            <p class="muted">An enterprise-grade, AI-powered procurement and inventory management platform designed to eliminate supply chain inefficiencies. Built with a modern microservices architecture, the system leverages machine learning to forecast demand and detect pricing anomalies, enabling data-driven decision-making for inventory managers and procurement officers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span>Next.js 15</span><span>Python</span><span>FastAPI</span><span>Prisma ORM</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>Redis</span><span>BullMQ</span><span>Tailwind CSS v4</span><span>TypeScript</span><span>Docker</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="clean">
            <li><strong>AI-driven forecasting:</strong> Integrated a Python/FastAPI service for real-time demand forecasting and price anomaly detection, reducing stockouts and over-procurement by surfacing high-risk supply patterns.</li>
            <li><strong>Microservices architecture:</strong> Decoupled Node.js/Express core business logic, Python for specialized AI workloads, and Next.js 15 for a high-performance, real-time dashboard.</li>
            <li><strong>Enterprise-grade inventory logic:</strong> Multi-warehouse tracking, manual stock adjustments, and reorder threshold monitoring.</li>
            <li><strong>Advanced procurement workflows:</strong> Dynamic purchase orders with multi-item lines and real-time totals, linking vendor management to stock fulfillment.</li>
            <li><strong>Robust data architecture:</strong> Relational schema with Prisma ORM and PostgreSQL, tuned for high-integrity procurement transactions and audit logging.</li>
            <li><strong>Modern UI/UX:</strong> Premium analytics experience with Tailwind CSS v4 and Recharts, glassmorphism accents, and responsive visualizations.</li>
          </ul>
